Description:
• Photograph of a painting by Roelant Savery of a landscape with men hunting a deer.

The incomplete annotation on the back only mentions 'Lose Akte 23'. It could belong to Kiste 1 (see RA 010 / 075) or Kiste 2 (see RA 010 / 210), but the subject doesn't seem to match those files. Maybe the wrong number was written on the back, and it should have been '24', meaning that it belonged to Kiste 1 - Lose Akte 24 (see RA 010 / 076).
